  skillDescription: "Giai \u0111o\u1EA1n k\u1EBFt th\xFAc, b\u1EA1n c\xF3 th\u1EC3
    r\xFAt X l\xE1 b\xE0i (X l\xE0 s\u1ED1 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\xF3 s\u1ED1 b\xE0i tr\xEAn
